'''Tamrikt''' neɣ '''Marikan''' neɣ '''Amirika''' d amenẓaw deg idis umalu n umaḍal. Tebḍa ɣef sin yeḥricen, [[Marikan n Ugafa]] id [[Marikan n Wanẓul]].
== Aẓar n wawal ==
Awal Marikan yekka-d si ''Amerigo Vespucci''. Isem-agi urant i tikkelt tamezwarut di 25 Yebrir 1507 deg yiwet n tkarḍa tarakalant . Yessufɣ-itt-id yiwen uressam n tkarḍiwin, Almani [[Martin Waldseemüller]] deg [[Saint-Dié-des-Vosges]], isemma amenẓaw amaynut ''America'' ilmend n [[Amerigo Vespucci]], imsilel aṭelyani.

