[[Kanada]], [[USA]], [[Groenland]] ([[Danimark]]), [[Miksiku]], [[Gwatimala]], [[Salvador]], [[Handuras]], [[Kusta Rika]], [[Panama]], [[Kuba]], [[Bermuda]] ([[Lingliz]]), [[Jamaika]], [[Haiti]], [[Republik n Dominik]], [[Puerto Riko]], [[Gwadilup]],[[Martinik]], [[Saint-Pierre d Mikelon]] (Fransa), Tigzirin i [[India]].

